麟darchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/lang-guide/chapters/types/other_types/path.mdﾙ@2495b92c75c07e3bdd2193ed244a965886d9d4aaf208a58274f24c644a6f1056､Path則Castsﾙ狼here is no 
