註拙ｹTitle: Path
Path: Casts
Content:
There is no 
``into path``
 command, but several commands can be used to convert to and from a 
``path``
:
``path expand``
``path join``
``path parse``
麟darchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/lang-guide/chapters/types/other_types/path.mdﾙ@74826f6c436a661f2585c2a6310646e4e38acff914f8caa14f278897c96540e1､Path胎#Common commands that can work with ﾙｰ``path``
``path (subcommands)``
See: 
``help path``
 for a full list
Most filesystem commands (e.g., 
``ls``
, 
``rm``
)
See: 
``help commands | where category == filesystem``
